Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.58,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.79,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san, your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.32,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu. Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.63,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san is sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.76,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.63,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It was getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:46.58,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of switching \Nit out with a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.45,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.02,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:04.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.37,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I keep getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with Monster-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:14.46,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(815,433)}What I Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.55,sora-main-top,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.00,sora-main-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,This really helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:18.16,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, \Nit was on my way to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Stop showing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:24.90,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.89,Station,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.83,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have time in \Nour third year to just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't know what to \Npresent at Hokubi Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any ideas, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.09,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Cows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She never grows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:19.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't really \Nchanged either, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.73,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:21.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're always pulling Yuzuki forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You were the mature one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.34,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's how you saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd look grown-up with glasses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.05,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done looking at the scenery?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:47.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to enjoy it more. \NI have to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.47,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Noel and Shione should have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We invited Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But she's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:04.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,"I have a prior engagement that day."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,"From years ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.16,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's just making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.29,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's really not honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.87,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Pain, pain, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.76,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.82,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.53,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach, I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.46,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Monster-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.55,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.50,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.22,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that Monster-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.39,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:17.82,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.37,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:20.23,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.59,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll help you treat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.75,Times,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Departure Times
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.88,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wait here for an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.10,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.86,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you wanted to savor it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's somewhere we can sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.19,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You brought this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we might need it \Nfor when we eat lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're eating here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I brought all the popular \Nitems on the shop's menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.84,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't make it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:33.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mom made it, but I was the\N one who arranged it nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.35,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:42.35,Toyono,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Toyono
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.59,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:42.35,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when we all brought our \Nlunches together like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.29,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,The observatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.11,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think Koharu forgot \Nher lunch that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:54.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,But Nonoka asked everyone \Nto share their dishes with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.57,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,And then Nonoka went overboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.83,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,and I ended up with the \Nmost extravagant lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.21,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.36,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.47,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is Monster-san going to get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.98,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.49,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:42.66,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's happy that \Nyou're so worried for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.52,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.81,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.27,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hold his arm down \Nso he doesn't squirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:50.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.67,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, Shorty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.39,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shorty? I'm Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go with Koharu and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.43,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They invited you, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.44,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the saucer from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.78,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:14.49,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How would you ever leave the town, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hold it down, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.45,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.50,Flowers,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are we there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:03.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.25,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, come on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you say a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This place is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How far do we have to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.58,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We're going the right way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm using the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.69,Map,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Here! \N{\fs16}Fourth row, \Nsixth from the right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for this landmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but I still can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call Dad and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.57,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I saw this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:44.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about anything, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:51.94,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She says to leave it to her, so let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.91,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It might not be not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.24,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.45,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think that does it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.98,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is Monster-san going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.73,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We did what we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.74,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.14,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not quite there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:30.25,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's bring \Nhim back into surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are we at the right place this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:40.51,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it was all Yuzuki's \Nfault that we got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some water, \Nso you can take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:57.38,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I forced you to let me come, but do \Nyou want to be alone with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:05.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:14.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this whole time, \NI've been afraid to see Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I still am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:21.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys hadn't said \Nyou wanted to meet my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I might not have been \Nable to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I've only seen her in pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but she seemed so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:34.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She was nice, and always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She'd always hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.59,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And she was warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:48.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But her hand was always cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:52.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago, right \Nafter we moved out of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:56.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that we moved so \Nthat Mom could get treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.05,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:09.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sad and lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:18.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's when I stopped remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's voice, her smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,my life living with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,that none of it ever \Nhappened to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wasn't miserable anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,My heart stopped aching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:46.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I forgot all the important things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:50.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, Koharu, Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:55.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And I hurt Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:03.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But you remembered us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:03.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:09.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom wouldn't forgive me the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't be proud of me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was never
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:18.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,a child that was worth being \Nproud of to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.81,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you here, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to see your mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That means you made up \Nyour mind to face all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like I did with Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.84,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.32,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.77,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept any arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.08,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I've been proud to be your friend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.74,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,since the observatory days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But can I have just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.19,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.97,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is it already that time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,They're like stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.67,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:04.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.64,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.44,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.50,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.43,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you talk to her \Nagain like way back when?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:32.38,Grave,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Grave of Ancestors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.05,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.81,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.14,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.64,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shione just—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san, we're all going \Nstargazing at the lake tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:02.03,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Has Shione met your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mom who gave me an \Nopportunity to be friends with Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.77,Grave,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(940,1)}Komiya Family
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to be her friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.23,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to smile more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.90,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look like that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.06,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you smiling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think your mom would \Nlike to see your smile, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Monster-san is going to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.70,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet he's thankful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,He's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.71,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,And Koharu won't be sad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:12.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu won't change him with \Nanother Monster-san now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.84,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But Koharu said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.91,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This Kirigon is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.66,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:26.06,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.77,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.34,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something, Yuzuki, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.47,Kirigon,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,800)}Kirigon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.66,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:41.64,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki did the draft drawing, \NI cut boards and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.47,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and we painted it with Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You were all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.82,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Your smile pushed me \Nforward a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That means
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:19:00.37,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,you took what your mom \Ntold you to heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, buck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.55,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.44,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably there with you about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.06,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.19,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to let Nonoka \Ngo instead this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.23,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Komiya Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:38.09,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't make it this \Nyear because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.81,sora-main,Koharu; Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.48,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.58,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.09,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thanking Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.65,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.72,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We worked hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.73,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be exactly the same, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.73,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san is all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:41.98,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.52,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine, does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:52.04,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the poster girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.91,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:58.37,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:03.01,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Not just yet, but we'll see a lot \Nof shooting stars on that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:07.45,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see, too, Shione-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.93,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:20.56,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Are shooting stars even more sparkly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.50,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.85,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch together when it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:24.94,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.95,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are watching you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:32.95,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:36.76,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because you're both smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:06.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:10.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:12.14,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shione here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:13.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.31,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:18.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione told me to tell you, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:21.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That she wanted to watch \Nthe meteor shower with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.18,sora-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to watch the \Nmeteor shower with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial Method{\i0}:
